In the INTEREST OF A.A., D.A., and N.A., Minor Children, C.C., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1693 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the juvenile court order terminating her parental rights to three children. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
